 step 3 :

 Click database:

flutter_db

Click SQL.

Paste:

CREATE TABLE users (
 id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(100),
 email VARCHAR(100),
 mobile VARCHAR(15)
);

Click Go. 



 Step 4:

 Go to:

C:\xampp\htdocs

Create folder:

flutter_api

Inside it create file:

insert.php

Paste this full PHP code:

<?php
header("Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *");

$connection = new mysqli("localhost", "root", "", "flutter_db");

if ($connection->connect_error) {
    die("Connection Failed");
}

$name = $_POST['name'] ?? '';
$email = $_POST['email'] ?? '';
$mobile = $_POST['mobile'] ?? '';

$sql = "INSERT INTO users (name, email, mobile)
VALUES ('$name', '$email', '$mobile')";

if ($connection->query($sql) === TRUE) {
    echo "Success";
} else {
    echo "Error";
}
?>

Save it  



